snippet.title: Quake - The Offering - [Unused Jam] - Map 03 - Neglected Network - [4K] - [100%]
snippet.description:
Quake Single Player Custom Map
Title Map 03: Neglected Network
Author : Greenwood
Release Date : 09.02.2021

Description from the Readme:
My submission for the "Unused Jam" ...basically a Base void map. I ended up using textures from all of the unused wads. Of course, stuff like doors came from id1, but the bulk is unused.

Download : Unused Jam
http://quakeworld.fi/files/mappacks/unusedjam.zip

Played with : AfterQuake Package:
https://fte.triptohell.info/downloads

You have a question or criticism, then write a comment!
